{"tid":144634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司機注意！　網傳「撞車黨」深水埗衝馬路博撞","createTime":"2017-03-05T14:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T10:33:05.000Z","uid":732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6830d11c181c4c293655624c3a5e456119725374","tid":144634,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"網上近日流傳內地流行的「撞車黨」，出現於本港。早前有司機以車頭的攝影機拍下驚險的一幕，一名路人多次無故衝出馬路，更疑似故意跌倒在地上，幸好另一名司機反應敏捷，即時避開，否則就可能釀成意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AfYgQjdNeD8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAfYgQjdNeD8&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ59ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=90b1c314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AfYgQjdNeD8</a><br />\n<br />\n根據網民在facebook群組「香港突發事故報料區」的片段，事件是發生於上月24日日間，一名身穿深色衫的途人在深水埗麗閣邨附近，由行人路走到馬路，在看準汽車前來時就「插水式」仆在地上。汽車司機即時轉線避開，並繼續行駛。而該名途人就自行起身，未有異樣。不過片段沒有交代該名途人的去向。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2Zr3zP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2Zr3zP.jpg&h=488d8a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該途人「插水式」仆在地上，還幸司機及時避開，未有釀成意外。（網上片段截圖）<br />\n<br />\n網民：累死司機<br />\n不少網民在看過片段後，都稱讚司機身手敏捷，避過一劫，又認為該名男子屬內地流行的「撞車黨」，即以訛稱自己被車撞傷要求司機賠償，從中敲詐司機一筆。有網民擔心「撞車黨」日漸流行：「今時今日唔裝夠八個車CAM（攝影機）全包圍錄影，真係唔好開車呀。」亦有網民表明本港司機不受這一套：「呢種人以為在大陸，可以俾錢搞搞掂呢？」"},{"pid":"bbc01c95effcc0265b46cb8592ad6d7d8e622410","tid":144634,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5045b19bd9ec7c1fdc964c68da3377d1d39635d0","tid":144634,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15104bcf27938cc26af07f08d9d4c501452516e7","tid":144634,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"屈撚到咩戇鳩， 個個裝車cam， 馬路又有cam<br />\n香港地週街都係人， 屈條毛<br />\n大陸狗唔熟香港先覺得屈到"},{"pid":"a1da431cfcb5d9fd895062ed8fd73517a106a1c6","tid":144634,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:29:12.000Z","msg":"其實我當乜都冇<br />\n車到佢報警 咁佢claim保險 我當運濟要整車<br />\n我都唔駛俾錢佢架"},{"pid":"dd28444be7d9b7923acc80c48f80917c3eb63b88","tid":144634,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"頂多咪叫佢報警囉<br />\n一話報警佢實走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edafb999e2067fb9456bc6deed1ac365cce0264","tid":144634,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plaxtonlbuspage/videos/1241251282579237/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplaxtonlbuspage%2Fvideos%2F1241251282579237%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ59ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=627b6e7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plaxtonlbuspage/videos/1241251282579237/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢單係呃錢定傻佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b421366a5d3c252ac696e597546ef6dead89d8b","tid":144634,"uid":84950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"撞咗就算最後你冇責任唔洗賠，<br />\n佢地入院都可以報車手獎，政府賠"},{"pid":"eb17408cde0c4e6e162ab1e7e2aeddd90c6aa1f1","tid":144634,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/432383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F432383.jpg&h=a2a53525&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8203665d816a57ec5bd621e5f1e19ce35c60a39","tid":144634,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:06:37.000Z","m